<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 - Page Not Found</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            background-color: #eaeaea;
            text-align: center;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            background-image: url(https://img.freepik.com/free-vector/blue-curve-background_53876-113112.jpg?size=626&ext=jpg&ga=GA1.1.1546980028.1702857600&semt=ais);
            background-size: cover;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #2c3e50;
            font-size: 3em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        p {
            color: #7f8c8d;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            margin-top: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        a {
            color: #3498db;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <section class="404">
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Oops! Something went wrong.</h1>
        <p>The page you are looking for might be under construction or does not exist.</p>
        <img src="your_custom_image_or_icon.png" alt="404 Error Image">
        <p>Return to <a href="/">home page</a>.</p>
    </div>
</section>

</body>
</html>
    